		{
			dependencies: ["44D8AACDA42FCF19"]
			description: [
				"In the quests of this modpack you will find some patterns that correspond to the following concepts:"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"&9# Colors"
				""
				"&rIn the techpack, a color pattern was adopted in order to facilitate the player's understanding, they are:"
				""
				"- &5Purple&r: Indicates the name of an item or a subtitle"
				"- &eYellow&r: tutorial and topics"
				"- &9Blue&r: simply highlight text"
				"- &aGreen&r: tips"
				"- &cRed&r: alert"
				""
				"&c⚠ Alert:&r(On certain occasions the colors may deviate from this pattern, but you will be warned when this occurs)&r"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"&9# Quest shape&r"
				""
				"The shape of a quest icon also has a meaning, they are:"
				""
				"- &9Rounded Square&r : Normal Quest"
				"- &9Circle&r: Optional Quest"
				"- &9Square:&r Second path"
				"- &9Gear&r: Important advancement&r"
			]
			icon: "minecraft:writable_book"
			id: "0D20C2E3C2E9E984"
			subtitle: "&5 Concepts of questing"
			tasks: [{
				id: "47F7555E4C4DAD1C"
				title: "Done"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
