		{
			dependencies: ["44D8AACDA42FCF19"]
			description: [
				"The modpack has its own shop, where you can buy raw materials, food, supplies, etc."
				""
				"It was made with the intention of avoiding grinding, but without being broken, so keep in mind that things are expensive"
				""
				"&e-&r You can access it through the inventory, in the upper left corner, or by clicking &9F4&r"
				"&e-&r The sales are Questlocked, that is, they will only appear when certain quests are completed."
				"&e-&r When you unlock a new sale, it appears normally in the shop, but with a description indicating which quest is necessary to obtain it"
			]
			icon: "kubejs:epic_techbuck"
